{"tid":150986,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"叫雞就雞蟲  咁叫莊呢？","createTime":"2017-03-10T13:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T17:38:40.000Z","uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c70c1560e5f0542a621a99aacc382e18bb5d67bf","tid":150986,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T13:12:51.000Z","msg":"科大電子工程系學生，涉因學生屬會的選舉宣傳活動問題，與競爭對手發生爭執，繼而動手。他今於觀塘法院否認兩項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，裁判官看控方呈上的傷勢圖後「嘩」了一聲，受害人的頸和肩膀有血紅色爪痕及紅腫。案件押後至3月16日開審，被告准繼續保釋外出。<br />\n<br />\n　　控方指有2名證人，而辯方透露將爭議受害人當時認錯被告，亦會有辯方證人，但稱短時間內未必聯絡上，裁判官指不是去「天山」找證人，著辯方盡快處理。<br />\n<br />\n　　控罪指，被告莊鈞絡（20歲）於2016年2月26日，在科大地下賽馬會大堂內，襲擊兩名事主造成他們身體受傷。據悉當日不同學生屬會招生，學生在場「叫莊」，惟競爭對手的攤檔「過界」，因而出手打對方。<br />\n<br />\n叫莊真係好惡呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6462d347a57bc955cbdc70984924e06df94703d","tid":150986,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T13:14:53.000Z","msg":"白痴仔"},{"pid":"117140a3699d738d00154739e6b4ffd66ffba46c","tid":150986,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T16:09:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>白痴仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3442782c5351eefa5b86ca12c42d97f476b871","tid":150986,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f05b6a2d7fcb583fcd3b9043c5511606e2d3641","tid":150986,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:09:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=